33
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:05,920
And another point I will tell you is always try to write the controller name before the action name,

34
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:13,270
because when you have to find out or you identify some action method, it is always inside a controller.

35
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:18,100
So that is why I try to write the controller name before the action name.

36
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,760
But even if you switch that, that is fine.

37
00:03:20,770 --> 00:03:25,990
It is something that I prefer and it is easier to read because of that.

38
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:31,390
I always write controller and then the action in that controller.

